{"in": {"title": "Questing Lores", "subtitle": "2. Jay's Tavern and Amnesia", "lines": ["NARRATOR: Fangs leads you down a rough dirt path, deeper into the city. You notice a few houses here and there of all different odd shapes and architecture, but the town seems to be asleep. You see the sun glint off a roof shingle that comes up to your knees.", "YOU: No way. It's a little house. What's inside?", "NARRATOR: A giant paw lightly swats your reaching hand away from the tiny door knob.&nbsp;", "FANGS: Manners! Don't trespass, twig legs.&nbsp;", "YOU: Okay! Twig legs? That's unwarranted. And I didn't realize", "FANGS: Yeah, yeah, yeah. Why else would someone make a house if not to live in it?&nbsp;", "YOU: (defensively) I guess I just thought it was a dollhouse.&nbsp;", "FANGS: Doll? We don't have that species here, I don't think. And we respect all species equally. \"Just a dollhouse.\"", "NARRATOR: Fangs sniffs, shaking his head at your backward culture. Then, he starts walking a little slower and with what looks like glint of terror in his eyes, shivers.", "FANGS: Mice are vengefulthey get in your clothes and pantry and furniture the gnawing sound from everywhere for just a few hours to destroy it all. And this guy's got a two story house. (shivers again) He's probably got a whole legion of children.", "YOU: (taken aback) Oh I see. Experience?&nbsp;", "FANGS: Let's not talk about it.&nbsp;", "NARRATOR: After a few more minutes, you arrive at a long rectangular building with swinging saloon doors. Fangs turns back to you, and twirls his tail in flourish.", "FANGS: At last. Welcome to the Joking Jay's Tavern.&nbsp;", "YOU: (cautiously following him in) Is this a bar?&nbsp;", "NARRATOR: Fangs doesn't respond to you, just leans over the massive, heavy-duty counter where a few other large cats are lounging, and waves over a bartendera small black bird with iridescent tipped feathers.", "FANGS: Can I haveoh, one swashbuckler salty ale?&nbsp;", "NARRATOR: You watch in awe as the bird flaps around and somehow manages to drag over a glass of ale as large as himself.", "YOU: Impressive.&nbsp;", "FANGS: Not really.&nbsp;", "YOU: (sighs) So, then. Is this your friend that might know how to take me back?", "FANGS: Oh yes, my friend. One second.&nbsp;", "NARRATOR: Fangs nods and takes a sip, cringes as he swallows, then leaps onto the counter roaring.", "FANGS: (x-loud) GeT the MANaGER! ThE mAnAGer!!", "YOU: (whisper) SHHHH! What aRe you dOinG?! Fangs, get down here! Fangs!&nbsp;", "NARRATOR: You've turned beet red, and glance around you but no one seems bothered. The bartender flits into the back of the bar.", "FANGS: What is this watered down glass of the scum of POND WATER?! ThE mAnAGer!!", "YOU: Please, Fangs! I'm sure it's not that bad. (muttering to yourself) He's like moody adolescent \"Karen\".", "FANGS: I HEARD THAT! And get thE mAnAGer, I say!&nbsp;", "NARRATOR: Not a moment later, the black bartender bird returns with another bird, a slightly larger bird with blue feathers and this metallic little tie around his neck.", "FANGS: Hey! You! This drink tastes like the juice of fermented seaweed! What kind of rubbish do you think you are serving to your esteemed guests?", "JAY: Nice to see you again too. You know, there's no need to make a scene whenever you want to see me.", "NARRATOR: Fangs plops back off the counter looking petulant.&nbsp;", "FANGS: Well, where's the fun in that?&nbsp;", "YOU: (turning to Fangs) You know, I'm growing more and more convinced that you really did drag me through that forest because you wanted to hear me scream.", "NARRATOR: Fangs turns to you, rolling his large yellow eyes.", "FANGS: This is my pal, Jay. Jay, this is twig legs.&nbsp;", "JAY: It's a pleasure. Want a lollipop, kid? Or a butternut crinkle?", "NARRATOR: From tucked under one wing, he pulls out a tray of papery, pastry looking cookies. You realize there is absolutely no way he could've fit something that large in the nook of his shoulder but you're past disbelief in most things now. But when from under the other wing, he launches a fist sized lollipop towards your face at major league pitching speeds, your jaw drops when it doesn't shatter against your skull but instead stopsinches from your face. And it hovers in the air.", "YOU: This is too much for one day.&nbsp;", "NARRATOR: You pluck the large lollipop out of the air with shaky fingers. You stare at it, still stunned. Why were you here again?", "JAY: (screeches) It's delicious, don't worry! Take a crinkle! Take one!&nbsp;", "NARRATOR: You take a crinkle. It melts in your mouth.&nbsp;", "JAY: (screeches) It's delicious, don't worry! Take a crinkle! Take one! And Starla, get the kid a glass of ale! My ale's the finest in the world. Fang's given you the wrong impression of it now, I'm sure. But it is strong and it is good.", "FANGS: Do you think that's a great idea, Jay? I don't know if twig legs can stand the wonder of your", "NARRATOR: You numbly take the glass and gulp it down, still dazed at the hovering lollipop.&nbsp;", "FANGS: Oh well. Too late now. I did come to ask you about something.&nbsp;", "NARRATOR: You feel a sharp pain flat across your forehead, and as if your center of balance was suddenly shifted forward. You grab onto the counter to steady yourself and shake the feeling away. You furrow your brows, trying to summon something up from your memory.", "YOU: Wait. Yes. That's what we're here for. What are we here for?&nbsp;", "FANGS: Right. I'm here to ask about the best way to exterminate the rodent population from our beautiful world.", "NARRATOR: At this point, you're not feeling so funny but just like you might've forgotten something. Fangs request doesn't sound quite right.", "YOU: Are you sure that's what we came here for?", "FANGS: Yes, twig legs! If I say that's what we're here for, that's what we're here for. We're going to war!", "NARRATOR: To be continued..."], "speaker_map": {"NARRATOR": "Matthew", "YOU": "Amy", "FANGS": "Brian", "JAY": "Justin"}}, "out": {"cache_id": "09a0da300ec2357471289ac36aa84251", "audio_objects": [["3d90566217cf298bb91e3880c0d1627b-fangs-leads-you-down-a-ro---", 0], ["076a22b199a9e7cb3e69148b0ead3bee-no-way--it-s-a-little-hou---", 0], ["fed7dc1f2f1a533e9da636fe2e6a0418-a-giant-paw-lightly-swats---", 0], ["be84047195c9a4bcc7abfd5710b16637-manners--don-t-trespass-----", 0], ["e89ffe2d293660361bd27067fa77d253-okay--twig-legs--that-s-u---", 0], ["0313911d409de87ea9a6a4ce78a2442c-yeah--yeah--yeah--why-els---", 0], ["7b2359cd45ba6da8625afe5f94c80b37--i-guess-i-just-thought-i---", 0], ["4bce3c9a53b81a371e8d7510a351ade2-doll--we-don-t-have-that----", 0], ["fe096eb47aa4fd93c81c37029361b72a-fangs-sniffs--shaking-his---", 0], ["5278bf4b5a7626454e4d25f8cd4569d1-mice-are-vengefulthey-get---", 0], ["2e2c4595eeb825a405b2d06b75ce70d6--oh-i-see--experience--", 0], ["d3003496ba77fb6c1430f4d0193427e7-let-s-not-talk-about-it--", 0], ["e360e859d37dcbd9e5b43130911d35db-after-a-few-more-minutes----", 0], ["005f4e763856d427815bb5634a1cc187-at-last--welcome-to-the-j---", 0], ["ce2b1cfd15db42c31bd3f103aa9ab94d--is-this-a-bar--", 0], ["1e522f4754d6903f59ec2328854e7d65-fangs-doesn-t-respond-to----", 0], ["6933b4a38e4b52af63a38b3e5e4ebd6c-can-i-haveoh--one-swashbu---", 0], ["a3a0bb9356f8713eb186c8773b744ff8-you-watch-in-awe-as-the-b---", 0], ["c09519480a4fca8a63cdef9bf526f4b1-impressive--", 0], ["b90bc231326b9baeb64b221e5666d00f-not-really--", 0], ["a128805104eb5f4c0109d1577b2ce0c8--so--then--is-this-your-f---", 0], ["30e15e37c974b493d8c0fe844d55dd2b-oh-yes--my-friend--one-se---", 0], ["bd1ebf407474c48a118b1c38ecebbc51-fangs-nods-and-takes-a-si---", 0], ["f590c9429db09be2443af5de915d18ab--get-the-manager--the-man---", 0], ["ae8efb87322152dd6e11fdd5ac77576b--shhhh--what-are-you-doin---", 0], ["d7a59abb233b3c650af8973442c163f3-you-ve-turned-beet-red--a---", 0], ["dfc2e4a7f82edb1e00bea8accc825402-what-is-this-watered-down---", 0], ["4ca6b1b9ab62bedd9e33c6de0049081f-please--fangs--i-m-sure-i-